    {
      "line": "Ah... a seeker of thought, not flame nor melody. Welcome to the Archive of Reason.",
      "background_sprite": "Backgrounds/StageTwo/Athena/Library.png",
      "left_sprite": "Characters/Transparent.png",
      "right_sprite": "Characters/Cecrops.png",
      "audio": { "path": "", "loop": false }
    },
    {
      "line": "I was told Athena's wisdom lies here. I need her guidance.",
      "background_sprite": "Backgrounds/StageTwo/Athena/Library.png",
      "left_sprite": "Characters/Player.png",
      "right_sprite": "Characters/Transparent.png",
      "audio": { "path": "", "loop": false }
    },
    {
      "line": "Many desire wisdom. Few are prepared to meet her terms. Tell me, child of war and nightâ€”what will you do with knowledge once you hold it?",
      "background_sprite": "Backgrounds/StageTwo/Athena/Library.png",
      "left_sprite": "Characters/Transparent.png",
      "right_sprite": "Characters/Cecrops.png",
      "audio": { "path": "", "loop": false }
    },
    {
      "line": "I'll use it to reach Olympus. To break my bond. To survive.",
      "background_sprite": "Backgrounds/StageTwo/Athena/Library.png",
      "left_sprite": "Characters/Player.png",
      "right_sprite": "Characters/Transparent.png",
      "audio": { "path": "", "loop": false }
    },
    {
      "line": "Purpose sharpens thought, but it must be tested. Here in this Archive, every scroll remembers who read it.",
      "background_sprite": "Backgrounds/StageTwo/Athena/Library.png",
      "left_sprite": "Characters/Transparent.png",
      "right_sprite": "Characters/Cecrops.png",
      "audio": { "path": "", "loop": false }
    },
    
    {
      "line": "Every tome whispers to those who fail to listen. Let us see if your mind is tempered enough to approach the goddess.",
      "background_sprite": "Backgrounds/StageTwo/Athena/Library.png",
      "left_sprite": "Characters/Transparent.png",
      "right_sprite": "Characters/Cecrops.png",
      "audio": { "path": "", "loop": false }
    },
    {
      "line": "So you're the gatekeeper?",
      "background_sprite": "Backgrounds/StageTwo/Athena/Library.png",
      "left_sprite": "Characters/Player.png",
      "right_sprite": "Characters/Transparent.png",
      "audio": { "path": "", "loop": false }
    },
    {
      "line": "Gatekeeper, librarian, judge. I watched Athens choose the olive tree over the sea. I've seen wisdom win and falter.",
      "background_sprite": "Backgrounds/StageTwo/Athena/Library.png",
      "left_sprite": "Characters/Transparent.png",
      "right_sprite": "Characters/Cecrops.png",
      "audio": { "path": "", "loop": false }
    },
    {
      "line": "You'll face eight riddles and questions. Pass, and I'll summon Athena. Fail... and you will walk away only with echoes.",
